Remove wrappers from chocolates. Heat oven to 350 degrees F and line muffin cups (2 1/2 inches in diameter) with paper baking cups. Prepare mix according to package directions. Fill muffin cups 1/2 full with batter and place chocolate in each center. Bake according to package directions. Remove from cups to wire rack. Cool completely. Tint frosting with red and yellow food coloring to make orange and frost cupcakes. Cut candies and decorate to make monster faces.